(219, 1, '2021-04-27 19:30:56', '2021-04-27 14:00:56', 'One Stop Dota Summer Dock League Season 1 concluded on 16th of April with Best of 3 ( BO3) Grand Finals.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-216\" src=\"http://onestopdota2.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/onestop_banner_image-300x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\nMotivate. Trust Gaming won the tournament with a score of 2-1.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Winner - MTG</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-179\" src=\"http://onestopdota2.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/766px-Motivate.Trust_Gaming_logo-300x235.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"157\" />\r\n\r\n2. Runner up - Dota Geniuses\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" src=\"http://onestopdota2.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/dg.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" />', 'One Stop Dota Summer Dock League Season 1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'one-stop-dota-summer-dock-league-season-1', '', '', '2021-05-03 17:25:12', '2021-05-03 11:55:12', '', 0, 'http://onestopdota2.com/?post_type=concluded&#038;p=219', 0, 'concluded', '', 0),
